Description:
  This path contains the portions of the chromium code used to drive h.264, VP9 and MJPEG decoders. It was forked
  from c53c9bb7825c3179a7e89607e8520438fb2bf627 and has been modified to drive the amlogic and VAAPI video
  decoders.
